---
const marks = [
	{ top: "6%", left: "3%", size: "5rem", rotate: "-14deg", opacity: 0.9 },
	{ top: "68%", left: "8%", size: "3rem", rotate: "10deg", opacity: 0.35 },
	{ top: "14%", left: "88%", size: "3.5rem", rotate: "16deg", opacity: 0.5 },
	{ top: "74%", left: "84%", size: "5.5rem", rotate: "-8deg", opacity: 0.7 },
	{ top: "40%", left: "94%", size: "2.25rem", rotate: "6deg", opacity: 0.3 },
	{ top: "2%", left: "45%", size: "2.5rem", rotate: "-6deg", opacity: 0.25 },
];
---

<section id="about" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-white py-28 md:py-36">
	<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0" aria-hidden="true">
		{
			marks.map((m) => (
				<img
					src="/Question Mark.png"
					alt=""
					class="absolute"
					style={{
						top: m.top,
						left: m.left,
						height: m.size,
						width: m.size,
						opacity: m.opacity,
						transform: `rotate(${m.rotate})`,
					}}
				/>
			))
		}
	</div>

	<div class="container-page relative">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
			<h2 class="text-balance font-display text-4xl leading-tight font-semibold text-black md:text-6xl">
				Now to answer your question: what is{" "}
				<span class="text-violet-ray">{"{"}remote ticket sales{"}"}</span>,
				exactly?
			</h2>

			<p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-balance text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold text-[#ff0894] md:text-xl">
				No, it's not some false "earn from your chair's warmth" scheme, affiliate marketing, or
				randomly calling people.
			</p>

			<p class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-5xl text-left font-sans text-xl leading-snug font-semibold text-black md:text-2xl">
				High-ticket remote sales is a highly sought-after skill by businesses selling
				$2,000–$10,000 premium services like coaching programs, enterprise software, real estate,
				high-end consulting, or investment opportunities.
			</p>

			<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-5xl text-left font-sans text-xl leading-snug font-semibold text-black md:text-2xl">
				This means you'll be working with already-established businesses, selling these products
				and services to people who are genuinely interested and want to speak with a real human to
				help them decide whether an offer is right for them.
			</p>

			<p class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-violet-ray md:text-3xl">
				And that's where you come in!
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
